Package ohos.multimodalinput.standard

Interface CommonEventHandle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    StandardizedEventHandle

    public interface CommonEventHandle
extends StandardizedEventHandle
    Provides methods for handling standard common events.

    Common events include the actions of showing a menu, sending, copying, pasting, cutting, undoing, refreshing, starting dragging, canceling, confirming, moving, going to the previous or next element, printing, and going back.

    Since:
    5
    See Also:
    StandardizedEventHandle
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.MultimodalInput#MULTIMODAL_INPUT
